properties.description: Posted by Freshwater1050 Fife Avenue, Palo Alto, CAThis 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is situated on a lovely tree lined street near downtown bordering Crescent Park. The home features a formal living room with large bay windows, recessed lighting and marble fireplace. A separate dining area opens up to the kitchen which boasts a breakfast bar and second informal breakfast nook. French doors lead to a lovely landscaped courtyard complete with gazebo, which is perfect for outdoor entertaining. Two bedrooms and a bath are located on the first floor off of the living room. A third bedroom with bath is located on the second floor across from the master bedroom suite. The master suite has coffered ceilings, a spacious walk-in closet and Jacuzzi tub. Other amenities included a separate laundry room with washer and dryer, stainless steel kitchen appliances, skylights and detached 1-car garage. A private side yard retreat and excellent Palo Alto Schools complete this beautifully appointed home. Drive-by 1050 Fife Avenue, Palo Alto and call (650-400-2918) agent for an appointment. ,500/month + ,500 deposit Short Term Lease Includes Gardner
